# Pi Auth Extension — OAuth Client Configuration
#
# All 50 providers work out of the box with built-in defaults.
# Use this file ONLY if you need to override with your own OAuth app registrations.
# Copy to .env and uncomment the values you want to override.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional overrides (defaults provided for all)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

